com.ibm.websphere.samples.activitysessions.ASContainerManagedEJB
Class ASContainerManagedEJBBean

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.websphere.samples.activitysessions.ASContainerManagedEJB.ASContainerManagedEJBBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.ejb.EnterpriseBean, javax.ejb.EntityBean
public abstract class ASContainerManagedEJBBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.ejb.EntityBean

The ASContainerManagedEJB CMP EJB Bean implements the EntityBean interface. It contains two instance variables that are both of type int. These are index, which is the key value for the EJB, and value.

Points to note about it's deployment are as follows

  • The bean will be deployed such that it's data is backed into a one phase datastore
  • Activation policy set to ActivitySession
  • Local Transaction Containment set to ActivitySession
  • Local Transaction resolution control set to ContainerAtBoundary
  • Transaction attribute is NotSupported
  • ActivitySession type of Container Managed
  • ActivitySession attribute set to Mandatory
